  "body": "introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15204\r\ncc @alwx \r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Set dark mode for the app\r\n2. Clear the history of a chat.\r\n3. Open any chat\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nThe top bar of the chat screen is displayed with two separate sections with different colors.\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/b314f318-b205-457f-bc53-420924af11d4)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nThe top bar of the chat screen should be displayed as a single unified section and matched to design\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1758-372971&t=kHyYjjz6mXjcc2H9-0\r\n\r\n### Devices:\r\n- Pixel 7a, Android 7a\r\n- Android Studio: Pixel XL API 29",
